@startuml UC_23_Create_Community
title UC-23: Create Community

|User|
start
:(1) Open Create Community;
:(2) Enter community name and description;
:(3) Choose community type and optional style media;
:(4) Submit the form;

|System|
:(5) Validate authentication and community name rules;
:(6) Create the community record;
:(7) Add the creator as the first member;
:(8) Return the new community;

stop
@enduml
